videos.name: Jev Vainsteins in Luxembourg, The Arch Summit
videos.description: The Arch Summit is tailored to bring together the corporate and startup world, giving both parties an opportunity to network and partner to drive innovation. The stage is built for innovation and entrepreneurial spirit where you have the chance to be inspired by industry leading speakers, compete to fund your business, network directly with corporate key decision makers and drive the change.
